<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9B03E7D61E3BE631A25751C0A9669D946597D6CF" class="external text" title="http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9B03E7D61E3BE631A25751C0A9669D946597D6CF" rel="nofollow">""CLEVER HANS" AGAIN.; Expert Commission Decides That the Horse Actually Reasons."</a>. The New York Times. 1904-10-02<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9B03E7D61E3BE631A25751C0A9669D946597D6CF" class="external free" title="http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9B03E7D61E3BE631A25751C0A9669D946597D6CF" rel="nofollow">http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9B03E7D61E3BE631A25751C0A9669D946597D6CF</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-01-02</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=%22CLEVER+HANS%22+AGAIN.%3B+Expert+Commission+Decides+That+the+Horse+Actually+Reasons.&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.au=The+London+Standard&amp;rft.date=1904-10-02&amp;rft.pub=The+New+York+Times&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fquery.nytimes.com%2Fmem%2Farchive-free%2Fpdf%3Fres%3D9B03E7D61E3BE631A25751C0A9669D946597D6CF&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Clever_Hans"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
